OL,3,CMan jailed for 8 years after
OL,4,C#2.4million of cocaine found in his car
OL,6,FA man from Glasgow has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto eight years in prison after
OL,8,Fpleading guilty to possession with
OL,9,Fintent to supply Class A drugs.
OL,11,F33-year-old Scott Tobin of Holmelea
OL,12,FCourt, Glasgow, was stopped by
OL,13,Fofficers near Penrith on November 5,
OL,14,Fwho found cocaine in his vehicle with
OL,15,Fa street value of #2.4million.
