OL,3,CMan jailed for 8 years after
OL,4,C#2.4million of cocaine found in his car
OL,6,FPolice had stopped the scaffolder as
OL,7,Fhe drove his Mercedes on the M6
OL,8,Fnorthbound. One officer told the court
OL,9,Fthat Tobin was "nervous" and
OL,10,F"shaking", and that when he was asked
OL,11,Fif there was anything of note in the
OL,12,Fcar "the colour drained from his face".
OL,14,FOfficers then found 30 rectangular
OL,15,Fblocks of a substance, later
OL,16,Fidentified as cocaine, in the boot of
OL,17,Fhis car.
