OL,3,CMan jailed for 8 years after
OL,4,C#2.4million of cocaine found in his car
OL,6,FCarlisle Crown Court heard that Tobin
OL,7,Fhad run up a #20,000 debt with HMRC,
OL,8,Fand had agreed to transport the
OL,9,Fpackage from Liverpool to Glasgow for
OL,10,F#2,500.
OL,12,FCallum Morris, mitigating for the
OL,13,Fdefendant, said: "He is very
OL,14,Fremorseful. He wants to apologise to
OL,15,Fthe court."
OL,17,FJudge Michael Fanning, who handed down
OL,18,Fthe eight year sentence, recognised
OL,19,Fthat Tobin had been "candid, open and
OL,20,Fhonest" with a probation officer about
OL,21,Fhis criminal conduct.
