OL,3,CMan jailed for 8 years after
OL,4,C#2.4million of cocaine found in his car
OL,6,FJudge Fanning continued: "The harm
OL,7,Fwould be significant if this (drug)
OL,8,Fhad ended up on the streets `
OL,9,Fsomething which you readily
OL,10,Fappreciate."
OL,12,F"You went into this with your eyes
OL,13,Fwide open. You took a calculated risk."
OL,15,FA spokesperson from Westmorland and
OL,16,FFurness' Community and Serious
OL,17,FOrganised Crime (CSOC) Unit said: "The
OL,18,Factions of the officers who stopped
OL,19,FTobin's vehicle that day have ensured
OL,20,Fmillions of pounds worth of drugs
OL,21,Fnever make it onto the streets.
